<plot>Learn to Speak Body: Tape 5 satirizes the language instructional video, but instead of teaching Burmese or Bambara, it examines the grammatical intricacies of body language. Yes, in just a few easy lessons you too can learn to speak body just like humans do, as we conjugate head position, analyze the accent of a hip, and become fluent in the psychosexual syntax of the slouch. (And no, there is no Tape 1-4.)</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?327804</url></doc>
